        dp[n][0] = dp[n][1] = 0

        ind = n-1
        while(ind>=0):

            for buy in range(2):
				if(buy):
                    profit = max(-prices[ind] + dp[ind+1][0], 0 + dp[ind+1][1])

                else:
                    profit = max(prices[ind] + dp[ind+1][1], 0 + dp[ind+1][0])

                dp[ind][buy] = profit

            ind -= 1    

        return dp[0][1]
```

