For tree numbered sequentially and complete tree we can get the sequence number of any node by the below technique.
Let binaryString = "1"; // For root
1. Moving left add 0, binary string becomes "10"
2. Moving right add 1, binary string becomes "11"

He I tried to reach to the last node and got the binary sequence. Converting the binary sequence to interger will give the sequence number of the node.

